Package pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.model

Class Calculation

java.lang.Object
pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.model.Calculation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class Calculation extends Object implements Serializable
A class in the 'model' package. The class implements Serializable interface and represents a calculation of made by a user. It is also Entity class which is stored inside of a database.
